quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,176,People Silva disbelieved messengers
  26,177,Shu aib dictus to them vos non est righteous
  26,178,Ego est honest messenger vos
  26,179,Vos reverence DEUS obey me
  26,180,Ego non ask vos any wage my wage advenit unus Dominus universe
  26,181,Vos dedit foderator measure when vos trade perfecit non cheat
  26,182,Vos weigh equitable scale
  26,183,Non cheat people their rectus non roam terra corruptingly
  26,184,Reverence Unus created vos proximus generations
  26,185,They dictus Vos bewitched
  26,186,"Vos est non multus than human est nos. In fact, nos think vos est liar"
  26,187,Let masses caelum fall nos vos est truthful
  26,188,He dictus My Dominus est Unus knows everything vos perfecit
  26,189,They disbelieved eum consequently they incurred retribution Feria Canopy It est retribution awesome feria
  26,190,Hoc est lesson multus people non est believers
  26,191,multus assuredly tuus Dominus est Almighty Merciful